{"tid":136170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2月27日之冷冷冷:用2分鐘睇晒各地新聞","createTime":"2017-02-27T01:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T00:52:27.000Z","uid":68591,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c4cff7997dbce591e8b0af05e95da3cb0638a4","tid":136170,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"早晨! 勁凍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每條新聞下面既link係新聞既sources,大家想進1步了解既可以入去條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港聞:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 特首選舉參選人林鄭月娥將公佈完整政綱，其政綱首章談及政制與一國兩制的實踐，重申現時不會重推《基本法》23條立法和政改，避免加劇社會矛盾。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131647046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131647046&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e2f70b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131647046&h=d4861922\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131647046</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 全國政協常委陳永棋透露，政協常委會會討論增補4名全國政協委員，當中包括特首梁振英。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131659666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131659666&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c9774f9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131659666&h=e48ad29c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131659666</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 前立法會主席曾鈺成的智庫「香港願景」建議中央委派人員駐港出任行政長官政治顧問，特首作出涉及中央事務的決定前須通過政治顧問向中央請示，而中央政府駐港機構則不介入任何由特別行政區政府管理的事務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1556259&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1556259%26target%3D2&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=29a92846\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1556259%26target%3D2&h=165ea999\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1556259&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 《成報》發聲明表示有管理層的寓所外被張貼具恐嚇及抹黑成分的單張，其住宅單位大門及牆上被淋紅漆，其已就此報警。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131655985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131655985&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=afaaf33a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131655985&h=7ff91bb2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131655985</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170227/00176_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2F00176_030.html&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c05b56bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170227/00176_030.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 中國移動香港因電力故障令數據及話音服務受阻逾兩小時，通訊事務管理局辦公室要求中移動於3天內就事故提交報告。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131669806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131669806&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d20d678f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131669806&h=df4f41af\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131669806</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 一架機師訓練用的小型飛機於馬鞍山飛行途中疑引擎故障最終急降樹叢並掛於6米高大樹上，教官與考生輕傷被困，被消防員救下送院。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131652506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131652506&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a0d1ed31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00002%2F1488131652506&h=ef590168\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00002/1488131652506</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170227/00176_007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2F00176_007.html&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a227df8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170227/00176_007.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1556295&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1556295%26target%3D2&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=60ac549f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1556295%26target%3D2&h=a611814f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=155629