nt.php%3Fid%3D1556070%26target%3D2&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c48b4133\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1556070%26target%3D2&h=d823d64d\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1556070&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170227/19941535?_ga=1.158203386.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170227%2F19941535%3F_ga%3D1.158203386.1316658954.1419942048&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=872f1e85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170227%2F19941535%3F_ga%3D1.158203386.1316658954.1419942048&h=c6a68000\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170227/19941535?_ga=1.158203386.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 中央組織部部長趙樂際在北京會見訪華的新加坡副總理張志賢，張志賢此番訪華預料將簽署最少19份合作協議。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00013/1488131733610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00013%2F1488131733610&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5eadbde9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170227%2Fs00013%2F1488131733610&h=3e152563\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170227/s00013/1488131733610</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 中國外交部發言人宣佈，國務委員楊潔篪將應美國政府邀請對美國進行訪問，並就中美關係及共同關心的問題與美方高級官員交換意見。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1556067&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2